MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-597. Hoover v. Gamblin.

Summit County, No. 15707. This cause, here on appeal from the Court of Appeals for Summit County, was considered in the manner prescribed by law. Upon consideration of the joint application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective February 14, 1994.
